annotations.title: Moonraker Cocktail - a Vintage Drink with Cognac, Kina, Absinthe & Peach Brandy

textContent:
1oz Brandy
1oz Kina l'Aero (or Cocchi Americano)
1oz Peach Brandy (or Apple Brandy)
 2 Dash  Absinthe
garnish Lemon Twist

Shake with ice. Strain into chilled Nick and Nora. Garnish Lemon Twist.
